#: ../../../guide-plugin-language.md:1
msgid "Adding Language Support via the Plugin Path"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guide-plugin-language.md:3
msgid ""
"This guide walks through adding full AST-aware language support to lang-"
"check. It uses **TinyLang** (the project's reference demo language) as a "
"running example."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guide-plugin-language.md:6
msgid "Overview"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guide-plugin-language.md:8
msgid "The plugin path gives a language first-class integration with lang-check:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guide-plugin-language.md:10
msgid ""
"**AST-aware prose extraction** -- tree-sitter parses the document, and a "
"Rust module walks the syntax tree to collect only the nodes that contain "
"human-written prose."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guide-plugin-language.md:13
msgid ""
"**Math exclusion zones** -- inline and display math are recognized by the"
" grammar and either skipped entirely or replaced with spaces (preserving "
"byte offsets so diagnostics map back correctly)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guide-plugin-language.md:16
msgid ""
"**Code block / comment skipping** -- fenced code, inline code, and "
"comments are pruned from the AST walk so they never reach the grammar "
"checker."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guide-plugin-language.md:18
msgid ""
"**Structural command filtering** -- commands whose arguments are "
"identifiers or metadata (e.g. `@import`, `@ref`) are distinguished from "
"commands whose arguments are prose (e.g. `@title`, `@note`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guide-plugin-language.md:22
msgid ""
"The end result is that lang-check only grammar-checks real prose, with "
"accurate source positions for every diagnostic."
msgstr ""

